HEADWORD: Transume
<hw>Tran*sume"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>transumere</ets>, <ets>transsumere</ets>, to take from one to
another; <ets>trans</ets> across + <ets>sumere</ets> to take.]</ety>
<def>To change; to convert.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
